hopobject.body: We used to work together awamedica contact number The focus here is on three Cs: calories, customization and choice. You can access nutrition information and create a customized meal from scratch by mixing and matching with My Meal Builder on mcdonalds.com. People often don't realize that you can easily customize a meal by making order requests including holding the mayo, requesting no added salt on French fries and choosing grilled over crispy chicken. These simple swaps can save hundreds of calories.
